===Etymology===
Cro-Magnon is the name of a [[cave]] in the [[Dordogne]], [[France]], where the first skeletons were found in 1868.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# The earliest known form of modern [[human]]s, ''[[Homo sapiens]]'', to be found in [[Europe]], dating from the late [[Paleolithic]].